<tr>
<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Can anyone tell me of a good spawn to hunt at lvl 8 for xp?<br>
I am looking for something that has a known spawning point and spawns every 6 minutes or so.<br>
Something that I can solo.<br>
If anyone know of a MOB like this, please let me know.<p>

I have tried hunting skeletons and Pumas in Steamfont, but they wander around too much, and I spend<br>
most of my time running around looking for them.<p>

Thanks.<p>

Gnome Wizard.</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
