<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Actually a great place to hunt solo at lvl 8 for a wizzie is the druid ring in Butcher Block.  The dwarf skellies will be blue to you and u can kill them fairly easily one at a time...they will not all agro to you at once.  There are 4 spawns there and you can just go to one at a time.  At about 50% mana you can take one down with just rooting and nuking.  I went from 8 to 9 there in just over an hour.  ( started with almost 2 bubs in though).  You can also stock up on bone stacks to sell to necroes or turn in at Kaladim for exp and faction.  Hope this helps anyone....Lawmann</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
